ComicInfo.Summary:
Trapped in a world not her own, in a place where blending in isn’t really an option, Skye is in a tough situation, and one she doesn’t have the experience of getting out of. Cut off from her world and her friends, she must use every instinct she has to survive long enough to hope to see her home again.
Don’t miss the next unexpected step taken in Skye’s ever-unfolding, electrifying journey!
